Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:19.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:22.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream about someone I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:29.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san really did come back after all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:32.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me something important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:33.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:37.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just give up on something like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:41.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm alone, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:23.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'll try going outside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even though it hurts to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:28.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:46.64,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(653,132)\c&H1F0C7D&}TAKEDA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:46.64,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(923,133)\c&H1F0C7D&}SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:38.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rest for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:44.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll get my usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the weird juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's that person,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:57.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the one who was living with us until the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:00.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:05.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She seems vaguely familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.58,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Episode 11
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the freeloader left?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:15.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he'll eventually come back if he has nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:18.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a tough time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:22.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying my best so that you could stay here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:22.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:27.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be taken to Tachibana's house someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:32.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I ignored you even though we lived together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:37.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I started to love you, it would be hard for us to separate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:41.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I always pushed away my feelings so that I would be fine no matter when you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:44.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was no point. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:48.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lie to myself anymore, so I've decided;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:51.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you my own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on my knees in front of\NTachibana's house the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, they finally gave in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:00.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:07.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that I'll do my best on my own and not cause trouble anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:11.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Misuzu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:17.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you really that sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:20.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you just had a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your legs won't move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:26.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:31.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that female doctor at the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:36.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No hospital can cure me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:42.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san and I discovered the reason for my illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:47.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self is in the sky, and she's carrying a burden by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:51.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason why my body won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:54.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You always spout these fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:05:00.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep on living like before, without worrying about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:01.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's live our separate lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:10.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why would you say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:13.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you angry because I left you alone all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:17.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to see a doctor, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:24.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But two are better than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:27.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:41.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it tasty next time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:47.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cooking never tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:54.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it doesn't taste good, children grow up eating their parents' cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:01.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:09.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that if we become close,\N you'll get sick too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:12.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that in your dream too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:23.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of getting sick at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:27.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get sick, I'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:31.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be proof that we've become close, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:49.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How short should I cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it up to you, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:19.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll cut it to where you look the cutest, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:24.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy, you have more wrinkles now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to shave your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:27.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You look young, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:33.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you came to an open house at school, everyone else's moms were older,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:38.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You answered a question wrong and started crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:39.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:42.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I had to show off for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:45.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I raised my hand even though I didn't know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:47.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you hit me in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you said your favorite phrase, "Gao".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Discipline, discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:55.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, Misuzu has grown up into a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:57.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown up quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:03.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You hardly ever say that phrase anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:12.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:14.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:20.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, it's easier this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:25.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to even it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the other side is too short!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:49.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to even out the left and the right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:02.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:04.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really short!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:11.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like a little girl again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:13.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy's girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start over again from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:21.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:21.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start from here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:25.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:26.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:36.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the summer festival is soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:39.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... That's right. I forgot all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go with you, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I'll take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:48.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I want to go to the beach too
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because I've never gone with you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:54.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a lot of places you want to go to, don't you, Misuzu-chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do a lot of fun things with you, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Let's do all sorts of fun things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:04.66,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\frz29.551\pos(501,337)\c&H120D86&}Picture Diary
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:04.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fill your picture diary up with fun things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:08.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:13.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember your smile, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:17.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always remember it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:23.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:44.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, you're up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:02.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd be strong with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:05.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy went far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:12.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your substitute mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:32.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From today, I'll try to restore your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:37.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right if I'm Aunt Haruko until the day you see me as your mother again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Now you can go outside with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts to walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what this wheelchair is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll push you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun playing cards by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:06.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll feel good to be outside in the sun where there are lots of fun things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:19.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is sizzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:23.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The cicadas are chirping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:24.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Noisy, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.42,0:12:28.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.85,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(717,231)\c&H607085&}TAKEDA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.85,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\c&H1F0C7D&\pos(929,231)\c&H607085&}SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:38.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:42.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, I'm your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:49.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, this child cannot be surrounded by too many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I left her with you in this quiet town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:57.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:59.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my child now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I already got your parents' approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my child,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:03.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,mine and Ikuko's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You give her to me when she gets in the way
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then come to get her when you remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:10.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this home exists for your convenience?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:13.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I leave her here with you where she gets sicker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop using such formal language!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hearing it creeps me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aunty, you're scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:22.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry for yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aunty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until just a little while ago, she called me Mommy all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:31.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come. Let's go, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say "thank you" to your aunty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:37.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Where's your "thank you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:40.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:40.58,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:44.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take Misuzu away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu has been alone all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:47.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it ours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:52.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've decided to stay with her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:56.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still going to push her around because of the trouble between us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:57.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:01.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too smart, so I don't know how to put it nicely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:06.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do know this – I want to be with her so much more than you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the absolute truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:16.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, do you want to stay with Aunty Haruko from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aunty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:18.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:20.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to keep living with her from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:22.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:24.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:31.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If at that time, she still says she doesn't want to stay with me... If she says that, I'll accept it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can take Misuzu away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:46.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I regain the time we've lost in just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:53.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-chan, you really like dinosaurs, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Maiasaura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:58.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means good mother dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh. It sounds like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Velociraptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means swift thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! That sounds like Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:12.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which one of us is the thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:20.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's only a short walk, so hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be cooler at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:28.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat our lunch box there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:30.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the lunch box that I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our lunch will go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:37.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are sweet egg rolls too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I made them because you asked for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:43.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this a fun day, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:44.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:47.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:48.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:50.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's going to happen to the lunch box that I made?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to play by yourself that much, then find your own way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:01.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:43.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:45.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known it all along;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:58.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not cut out to be a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:16:59.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What I've been doing isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:05.29,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:07.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:09.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:14.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:15.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:16.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cicada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll catch it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the cicada-catcher-aunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cicada-catcher-aunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:26.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A scaredy-cat like you needs one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:28.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:29.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:32.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:41.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can play without worrying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:44.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right for Aunty to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:01.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:09.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not going to ask for much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:13.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be happy if I can just stay with you all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:16.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all that I wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:32.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the day I promised Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That fool. He'll come to ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:39.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then you'll say you want to go with him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:43.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll say you don't want to stay with me anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summer break is a long way from ending,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:56.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but our time together ends today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:01.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:02.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:04.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:11.50,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(669,356)\c&H000B20&}TAKEDA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:11.50,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\c&H1F0C7D&\c&H000B20&\pos(954,356)}SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:10.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one last place I want to take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:11.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a bit more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:21.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, it's the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:22.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:33.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many years it took for the two of us to come here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:38.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We could have enjoyed this beautiful view any time we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:41.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly were we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:51.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:56.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's heavy. It's been a long time since you carried her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:59.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you that she's grown this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:00.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:05.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:07.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She loves this stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:10.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll calm down and sleep if she's holding this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:14.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's still whining, give her this to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her favorite juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:17.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:29.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your princess is leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:41.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:06.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:16.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:18.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:26.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:30.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:46.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, the two of them talked for a long time in the sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:52.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring a doctor I can trust, so will you let her be examined?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:57.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally realized that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:02.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the person who'd been with Misuzu all this time was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:05.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Misuzu's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:42.93,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(500,900)\fs51\shad2.25\pos(641,293)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:42.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:46.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were pure white wings, and I was flying through the sky.
